AddressInfo.Title: Circle K Boone
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Activation required via Circle K Charge USA mobile app for iOS or Android or via contactless / chip card or Apple Pay / Google Pay supported via credit card terminal.

Two dual CCS 180kW units - 90kW per port when charging simultaneously on the same unit or 180kW for single vehicle.

More info at http://CircleK.com/Charge

Connections.Comments: Two stations capable of 180kw with two CCS connectors each. The stations split the 180kw output between two simultaneously charging vehicles.
